  {
    "title": "I guess we all have that one friend who\u2019s as calm as this guy\u2014totally unbothered...",
    "description": "I guess we all have that one friend who\u2019s as calm as this guy\u2014totally unbothered by the shooting at the White House Correspondents\u2019 Dinner. While the room descended into chaos and Trump was rushed to safety, this man just kept eating. The shooting left one Secret Service agent wounded, and yet, the gentleman stares straight ahead and takes another bite, even as an armed security officer clutches his weapon on the stage where Trump had been just moments before.",
